text: Jerry Ahrlin, born 15 January 1978 in Östersund, Sweden, is a Swedish cross- country skier. ==Trophies== * Marcialonga winner of 2007, 2009 and 2011 * Tartu Maraton winner of 2007 and 2011 * König Ludwig Lauf winner of 2013 ==References== ==Other websites== * FIS website Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish skiers
